Dataset Source

Kaggle Credit Card Fraud Detection Dataset:
https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/miadul/credit-card-fraud-detection-dataset

-- Dataset: 999 cardholders · 693 merchants · Jan 2019 – Dec 2020
-- Each row is one transaction. Key fields: timestamp, amount, merchant
-- category, cardholder home coordinates, merchant coordinates, date of
-- birth, and a binary fraud label (is_fraud = 1 means confirmed fraud).

